Dear JUnit devs,
I'm a researcher from UZH and my team and I are conducting a study on
Lambda Expressions and Functional Interface in APIs. JUnit project is one
of our targets and we would gather some information and opinion about this
topic from you. So I would be really happy if you filled the survey at the
following link:

https://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/4781913/704005e13cdb

Kind Regards, Fernando Petrulio.
